data.description: Exceptionally well maintained home in the Henderson Country Club area. This development is surrounded by 3 club fairways & holes. Just minutes from I-85, Maria Parham Medical Center, shopping and dining. This home has a spacious living room with a see-thru fireplace to the warm and inviting family room. The kitchen has some of the most beautiful granite counter tops you'll ever see & nice breakfast area. Your master suite has a trey ceiling, jetted tub, separate shower & dual vanity, 2 car garage & 2 tiered deck w/ natural gas grill & fire pit, new 25 year shingles installed October, 2023.
